headline: This Magnificent High-Yield Dividend Stock Just Became an Even Better Buy
summary: Medtronic's revenue growth has been relatively unimpressive in recent years.  There are other reasons to invest in Medtronic, including its rock-solid dividend program.  Medical device specialist Medtronic (NYSE: MDT) has not performed well over the past five years; the stock has significantly lagged broader equities.
